{"tid":2109290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"rthk 721 一年特輯 影到個個便衣 點幫佢宣傳好？","createTime":"2020-07-15T06:42:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T15:25:20.000Z","uid":42246,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"c2414641203b7c976b6629b58d748715d08c8582","tid":2109290,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T06:42:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GgUneJy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGgUneJy.png&h=16c061c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港台節目《鏗鏘集》昨晚播出 7.21 元朗襲擊一周年專題，透過重組多段當日拍攝片段、車牌查冊及走訪當日在場人士，發現當晚在元朗西鐵站聚集及襲擊市民的白衣人，部分人早上及傍晚已在開始聚集；<span class=\"red\">有鳳攸北街（俗稱雞地）的商戶閉路電視拍攝到，當日傍晚白衣人在場聚集期間，更一度有數名手持疑似委任證、懷疑是便衣警員的男子，在鳳攸北街來回十數次，但對現場手持木棍及國旗的白衣人未有制止。</span><br />\n<br />\n《鏗鏘集》記者先後向元朗警區指揮官何鎮宗及警察公共關係科查詢，對方均未確認或否認手持疑似委任證人員是否便衣警察。警察公共關係科僅重申，警方正在積極調查案件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">最重要 入去YouTube 比like 同留言支持rthk</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/or4B7NpHwbY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2For4B7NpHwbY&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu34WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=f6ece1c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/or4B7NpHwbY</a>"},{"pid":"bac251fbb3a4a24ecf690f1b49144fb4cca1e6d4","tid":2109290,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T06:44:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e64cfc8ceefbafa120acbb2dab8acecfe9908865","tid":2109290,"uid":42246,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T06:44:55.000Z","msg":"已經60萬點擊率 同5500留言<br />\n大家再去推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80abd5729723e0aeaa7fb045e0f2ab652a13972e","tid":2109290,"uid":160373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T06:45:10.000Z","msg":"班狗又會講咩大話?<br />\n定扮都唔扮, 話你地繼續查就違反國安法?"},{"pid":"02a27b6a5c74a5cf35ade350309a275cf0564c08","tid":2109290,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T06:45:44.000Z","msg":